additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Use only as directed. Misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling the contents can be harmful or fatal. Help stop inhalation abuse. Some hard surface may become damp when sprayed. Avoid slips and falls. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Do not spray toward face. If eye contact occurs, rinse well with water. If irritation persists, get medical attention. Do not expose to heat or open flame.
